# Google Analytics Tag

This portfolio uses Google Analytics (gtag.js) with tracking ID `G-G1YQQEQF4E`.

The gtag snippet is placed in `index.html` immediately after `<head>`. Since this is a single-page React app (SPA) with HashRouter, all routes share the same `index.html` — no additional per-page gtag insertion is needed.

However, if a **new standalone HTML page** is ever created outside the React SPA, the following snippet MUST be added immediately after `<head>`:

```html
<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
<script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-G1YQQEQF4E"></script>
<script>
  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
  gtag('js', new Date());
  gtag('config', 'G-G1YQQEQF4E');
</script>
```
